nodes.text: A Selkath Padawan took part in the First Battle of Ruusan alongside another Selkath Padawan under a Cerean Jedi Master in the Army of Light. He or she was choked to death by Lord Kopecz, while the other was fatally struck by Kopecz's Force lightning.
